pageContext.claim: “China is big -- buying again. You see that China is buying very big...A lot of people don't like to talk about that, but China is in the market buying very big --agricultural. ”
pageContext.analysis: China is buying a some agricultural goods in an effort to show good faith ahead of the upcoming trade talks. They previously froze all agricultural purchasing in August 2019. Overall, China purchased nearly two-thirds fewer agricultural products in 2019 than in previous years.
